---
title: Sequence Diagram - Chatbot Konfirmasi Pembayaran
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Tamu
    participant UI as Halaman /chatbot
    participant API as /api/chat
    participant LLM as Gemini 2.5
    participant Tool as Tool confirmPayment
    participant DB as Supabase

    Tamu->>UI: "Saya sudah transfer kode BK123456"
    UI->>API: POST messages
    API->>LLM: stream + tools
    LLM->>Tool: confirmPayment(bookingReference, amount, method)
    Tool->>DB: SELECT id, total FROM reservations WHERE booking_reference = ?
    DB-->>Tool: { reservationId, expectedTotal }
    alt Booking tidak ditemukan
        Tool-->>LLM: { success: false, error: "Kode tidak valid" }
    else Booking ditemukan
        Tool->>DB: INSERT INTO payments (reservation_id, amount, method, status='confirmed')
        DB-->>Tool: { paymentId }
        Tool->>DB: UPDATE reservations SET status='paid' WHERE id = ?
        DB-->>Tool: ok
        Tool-->>LLM: { success: true, message: "Pembayaran tercatat" }
    end
    LLM->>API: Stream balasan
    API-->>UI: Konfirmasi sukses + e-receipt
    UI-->>Tamu: Tampilkan pesan + ringkasan
